This paper deals with image segmentation using neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of recurrent neural networks (RNNs), which falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of parallelization on GPUs, which is a topic in parallel computing (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
